Name: Lee Truck Broker, Inc.
Description:
LTB Logistics is a full service third party logistics provider located in Stuttgart, Arkansas, that can meet any supply chain need from the production line to the store shelf for customers in all 48 continental United States plus Canada and Mexico. Services include FTL (Full Truck Load), and Intermodal transportation for refrigerated, dry, flatbed and bulk shipments, as well as specialty services for overweight, over-dimension, and time sensitive shipments.

LTB Logistics also provides dry and temperature controlled warehousing, cross-docking, and inventory management services, and offers logistics training and consulting, management of payables and receivables, payroll administration, and staffing assistance in the transportation industry.

The core values of the company are honesty, integrity and the consistent pursuit of excellence. Lee Truck Broker's mission is to provide customers with focused, innovative, and unsurpassed supply chain solutions at the best price while striving to keep vendors financially viable in a volatile and unpredictable market.
